{{item:1413}} {{item:3742}}{{item:3071}}  {{item:3748}} ( {{item:3139}} or {{item:3156}}  or {{item:3102}} ) and {{item:3111}} though sticking a ga in is a good idea if they are well coordinated, don't substitute boots though since shaco still needs to be mobile to be shaco.
